c: 9
v: 91
t: "Idoolaay inti maleelaay lakmisa maraay tumaleelak yattacceem gee waa maral jihaadak daffeyak Raaqaanamah dambi mayan, usun Yallaa kee kay farmoytah iimaan kee meqe taamá cagliseenik, meqem abbaasita maray malkit- le jihaadak Raaqaamah ken elle kataatan giti mayan, Yalli dambi cabti-li xuwawli"